texts.text: >A few days later...

*Sigh*
Where are they...?
We looked all over the Hideout...
At this point, it feels like they didn't get lost in here.
Then we might not be able to find them...
But everyone said they remember bringing their stuff here.
So then... Someone deliberately hid them somewhere?
Has anything else disappeared since we started looking?
But come to think of it... Huh? What was that thing...?
Wait... Oh, no way?!
Huh?! What is it, Nadja?!
I... I think I know who did it...!
I'll whisper it to you. It'll be our little secret...!
Oh, wow... Now that you mention it...!
I don't know if I'm right... I definitely could be wrong but...
We need to see and lay a trap to make sure we get the right perp.
This might work...
>The next day...
Still no luck...
Maybe look around the Hideout?
Sure... W-wait...!
Newbie left this here again...
What is it? Oh, that's a nice pen!
It's their pen.
They're not as smart as they look and say they keep losing it.
My boss is kinda like that too.
She'll say she left something in one place, but it'll show up in a completely different place.
But we need to keep looking as best we can!
We need to keep trying today too!
>Later that night...
Hey, it's here. It's really a pretty pen.
I can't wait to see the look on their faces this time.
*Snicker*
*Growl*
...! W-what's that noise?
*Roar*
*Scream*
>*Rustle*
W-what now? Who's there?
That's it! I need to get out of here...!
You!
>*Crash*
W-what is this? It's like a glass lantern...!
I'm trapped?!
What the hell?! Let me out!
It was really you, Pixie?
Oh...
You fell right for it.
Bait and switch!
Hook, line and sinker!
All that noise coming from the living room at this time of night...
It's just you kids. Yo, I thought a thief got in or somethin'.
It really was a thief.
Say what?
I'm not a thief! It was just a prank!
Hmmm? Yo, what's this about?

*Laugh*
That's priceless!
This isn't funny!
Yeah! What the hell's going on here?!
That thing was hiding all their stuff and making them look for it!
Like I said, it was just a prank...
I gave everything back, didn't I?
A remorseless thief. Fuse it with anything you like, Vagit.
Eek!
But how did you figure it out?
I would like to hear as well!
Uhh... The first thing that I thought was weird
was when I heard Pixie was over at the Hideout.
I was still in the forest.
I see...
Pixie did know where you were at the time.
She knew I wasn't at the Hideout but still went over there.
and said something about Shiori's outfit being "cute",
or Rika's gun just being a "toy".
We never said anything about what we were looking for...
The perp would've known what was taken, right?
Which is why we became suspicious.
So we laid a trap to confirm.
Something that could easily be taken and hidden away.
We did a stakeout while everyone was asleep.
First, I made myself a disguise!
We tricked the perp into taking the bait and run into our trap.
Kazufumi's lamp for catching demons came in handy here!
Ah... And you trapped Pixie inside this lamp.
Magnificent! They really pulled one over on you, Pixie!
Looks like you lost this time.

*Grumble*
Playing tricks is what I do though...
I apologized and gave everything back! LET ME GO!
Is everyone okay with that?
Sure. I don't see why not.
I agree. We'll keep a closer eye on things in the future.
Shiori...?
I think she needs a little more punishment, but... Fine.
(She's softer than she looks...)
But there's no next time. We can Fuse you with something gross.
Eek!!

*Sigh*
I'm tired...
Me too... But I'm glad we got everything back.
Nadja, Kabuso and Jack the Ripper.
Thank you very much.
Without them, we'd still be up a creek without a paddle.
Yeah... I guess they did alright.
I... I got to help Vagit?!
Da. Spasiba, Nadja.
Me too, boss?! How'd I do?
You... Uh... You did well...
Haha!! Yay!
Jack the Ripper.
Don't mind me. They just dragged me into their mess.
You left yourself open. This gun has steady sights and little recoil.
You gun-crazy bitch!! I'll kill you!!!
Hey, no fighting here...!
Ahh! Run!
Not good enough, Jack!
Seriously, take it outside if you're gonna keep fighting!!
